# Test files must never be deployed as Vercel Serverless Functions.
# Every api/*.ts becomes a function and counts against the plan's function
# limit (Hobby = 12). The trips test files (api/*.test.ts) were being turned
# into functions, pushing the count to 14 and failing the deploy at the
# "Deploying outputs" stage. Tests run in CI (smoke/visual), never on Vercel.
*.test.ts
*.test.tsx
